        "level": "hard",
        "type": "bridge",
        "generated_trace": {
            "thought": "Thought: The question asks for the location of the base of one of the three main British intelligence agencies. The provided context mentions three main agencies: the Secret Intelligence Service (MI6), the Security Service (MI5), and the Government Communications Headquarters (GCHQ). The context also states that GCHQ is \"Based in 'The Doughnut' in the suburbs of Cheltenham\". This directly answers the question.\n",
