        "generated_trace": {
            "thought": "Thought: I need to compare the birth dates of Odysseas Elytis and Cornel West.\nOdysseas Elytis was born on November 2, 1911.\nCornel West was born on June 2, 1953.\nComparing the years, 1911 is earlier than 1953. Therefore, Odysseas Elytis was born first.\n",
