        "type": "bridge",
        "generated_trace": {
            "thought": "Thought: The question asks for the year Jocelyn Bell Burnell's thesis supervisor was awarded the Eddington Medal.\nFirst, I need to identify who Jocelyn Bell Burnell's thesis supervisor was. The context states: \"As a postgraduate student, she discovered the first radio pulsars while studying and advised by her thesis supervisor Antony Hewish\". So, Antony Hewish is the supervisor.\nNext, I need to find when Antony Hewish was awarded the Eddington Medal. The context about Antony Hewish states: \"He was also awarded the Eddington Medal of the Royal Astronomical Society in 1969.\"\nTherefore, Antony Hewish was awarded the Eddington Medal in 1969.\n",
            "answer": "Action: Finish[1969]"
