        "generated_trace": {
            "thought": "Thought: The question asks about the main product type of the company that owns Kerrygold Irish Cream Liqueur.\nThe context states: \"the trademark is owned by Kerrygold under Ornua, previously known as the Irish Dairy Board.\"\nIt also states: \"Ornua ... is an Irish agri-food co-operative, which markets and sells dairy products on behalf of its members; Irish dairy processors and Irish dairy farmers. The co-operative is Ireland\u2019s largest exporter of Irish dairy products and owns the Kerrygold butter brand as well as Kerrygold Irish Cream Liqueur.\"\nThis indicates that Ornua owns Kerrygold Irish Cream Liqueur and Ornua mainly sells dairy products.\n",
            "answer": "Action: Finish[Dairy products]"
