            "thought": "Thought: The question asks for the name of a policy that favors disadvantaged groups, and it explicitly states that Black Economic Empowerment (BEE) is a form of this policy. The provided context defines \"Affirmative action\" as \"the policy of favoring members of a disadvantaged group who suffer or have suffered from discrimination within a culture.\" It also states, \"Black Economic Empowerment (BEE) ... It is a form of Affirmative action.\" Therefore, the answer is \"Affirmative action.\"\n",
            "answer": "Action: Finish[Affirmative action]"
        }
    },
