        "gold_answer": "Ice King",
        "level": "medium",
        "type": "bridge",
        "generated_trace": {
            "thought": "Thought: The question asks if John Kassir and Tom Kenny both voiced the same character.\nThe first part of the context mentions \"the antagonistic Ice King (voiced by John Kassir)\" in the pilot short.\nThe second part of the context mentions \"The Ice King is a character... The character is voiced by Tom Kenny\" in the series.\nSo, John Kassir voiced the Ice King in the pilot, and Tom Kenny voiced the Ice King in the series. Therefore, they both voiced the character \"Ice King\".\n",
