        "type": "bridge",
        "generated_trace": {
            "thought": "Thought: The question asks for the name of the pageant since 1996, for which John Martin & Co. was responsible.\nThe first paragraph states: \"Johnnies, owned by the prominent Hayward family for the majority of its existence, became an Adelaide icon, responsible for the famous Adelaide Christmas Pageant.\"\nThe second paragraph states: \"Since 1996 it has been known as the Credit Union Christmas Pageant.\"\nCombining these two pieces of information, John Martin & Co. was responsible for the Adelaide Christmas Pageant, and this pageant has been known as the Credit Union Christmas Pageant since 1996.\n",
            "answer": "Action: Finish[Credit Union Christmas Pageant]"
        }
    },
