        "level": "medium",
        "type": "bridge",
        "generated_trace": {
            "thought": "Thought: The question asks for the title of Rudyard Kipling's book where Shere Khan is the main antagonist. The provided context explicitly states: \"Shere Khan (Hindi: \u0936\u0947\u0930 \u0916\u093e\u0928 ; Urdu: \u0634\u06cc\u0631 \u062e\u0627\u0646\u200e ) is a fictional Bengal tiger and the main antagonist of Rudyard Kipling's \"Jungle Book\" and its adaptations.\" This directly answers the question.\n",
