        "gold_answer": "American Horse (Oglala Lakota: \"Wa\u0161\u00ed\u010du\u014b T\u021fa\u0161\u00fa\u014bke\" in Standard Lakota Orthography) (a/k/a \"American Horse the Elder\") (1830\u2013September 9, 1876) was an Oglala Lakota warrior chief renowned for Spartan courage and honor.",
