        "level": "medium",
        "type": "bridge",
        "generated_trace": {
            "thought": "Thought: The question asks what Italians call the sauce in a BiFi Carazza.\nThe context states that BiFi Carazza is filled with \"salami, cheese, and pizza sauce\".\nThe context also states that \"Tomato sauce (also known as Neapolitan sauce, and referred to in Italy as Salsa di pomodoro)\".\nPizza sauce is a type of tomato sauce.\nTherefore, Italians would refer to the pizza sauce in BiFi Carazza as \"Salsa di pomodoro\".\n",
            "answer": "Action: Finish[Salsa di pomodoro]"
        }
    },
